## Day 50: Major Milestone – 50 Days of Cybersecurity Learning

### 🎯 What This Means

Today marks **50 days in my cybersecurity journey**.
Not perfectly consistent — but real, honest progress.

There were days (even weeks) where I didn’t post or build anything.
But I didn’t quit — I came back.

---

