### 🔥 Biggest Realization

It’s not about how much you do every single day —
it’s about **how well you understand and apply what you learn**.

Consistency matters, but **depth matters more**.

---

### 💪 What Changed in Me

* I stopped chasing perfection and focused on progress
* I started thinking in terms of **attack surfaces & risks**
* I learned to come back even after breaks
* I became more practical, not just theoretical

